# üöÄ Re Plastic Innovations - Salesforce Lightning App Configuration

This document describes how the custom objects in the **Re Plastic Innovations** project are integrated into a custom **Lightning App** using the Salesforce App Manager.

---

## üì¶ App Overview

- **App Name:** Re Plastic Innovations
- **Developer Name:** Re_Plastic_Innovations
- **App Type:** Lightning Experience
- **Navigation Style:** Standard Navigation
- **App Icon:** ‚ôªÔ∏è (Optional custom branding)
- **Primary Use Case:** To manage the lifecycle of plastic waste collection, recycling, product inventory, orders, and restock processes.

---

## üß© Included Tabs (Objects)

| Tab Label           | Object API Name                                       | Purpose                                         |
|---------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------|
| Plastic Waste        | `Re_Plastic_Innovations_Plastic_Waste__c`             | Track collected plastic waste and its details   |
| Recycling Centers    | `Re_Plastic_Innovations_Recycling_Center__c`          | Manage recycling facility information           |
| Recycled Products    | `Re_Plastic_Innovations_Recycled_Product__c`          | Monitor recycled products and stock levels      |
| Orders               | `Re_Plastic_Innovations_Order__c`                     | Handle customer orders of recycled products     |
| Restock Requests     | `Re_Plastic_Innovations_Restock_Request__c`           | Trigger inventory restocking workflows          |

---

## üë§ User Profiles & Permissions

| Profile/Role        | Tabs Access                                      |
|---------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| Recycling Center Ops| Plastic Waste, Recycling Centers                 |
| Inventory Manager   | Recycled Products, Restock Requests              |
| Sales Representative| Orders, Recycled Products                        |
| System Admin        | Full access to all tabs and objects              |

---

## ‚öôÔ∏è Setup Instructions (For Admins)

1. Navigate to **Setup > App Manager** in Salesforce.
2. Click **"New Lightning App"**.
3. Configure:
   - App Name: `Re Plastic Innovations`
   - Developer Name: `Re_Plastic_Innovations`
   - Select standard navigation.
   - (Optional) Upload custom app icon or select a standard one (e.g., ‚ôªÔ∏è).
4. **Add the following tabs** in the "Navigation Items" section:
   - Plastic Waste
   - Recycling Centers
   - Recycled Products
   - Orders
   - Restock Requests
5. Assign the app to relevant **profiles** and **permission sets**.
6. Save and Activate the app.

---

## üìå Summary

The *Re Plastic Innovations* Lightning App centralizes operations for managing environmental sustainability initiatives within Salesforce. It allows role-based access to custom objects and automation through a user-friendly UI.

